{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/SourceRef","doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/SourceRef\/SourceProtocol-Implementations"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/SourceRef\/set(readyTime:)"},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets a source to be dispatched when the given monotonic time is"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"reached (or passed)."}],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Instance Method","externalID":"s:4GLib14SourceProtocolPAAE3set9readyTimeys5Int64V_tF::SYNTHESIZED::s:4GLib9SourceRefV","extendedModule":"GLib","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"set"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"readyTime","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@gint64","text":"gint64"},{"kind":"text","text":")"}],"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"GLib"}],"title":"set(readyTime:)"},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"set","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"readyTime","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@gint64","text":"gint64"},{"kind":"text","text":")"}]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If the monotonic time is in the past (as it","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"always will be if "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"readyTime"},{"text":" is ","type":"text"},{"code":"0","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":") then the source will be"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"dispatched immediately.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"readyTime"},{"type":"text","text":" is "},{"code":"-1","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" then the source is never woken up on the basis"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"of the passage of time.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Dispatching the source does not reset the ready time.  You should do","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"so yourself, from the source dispatch function.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that if you have a pair of sources where the ready time of one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"suggests that it will be delivered first but the priority for the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"other suggests that it would be delivered first, and the ready time"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"for both sources is reached during the same main context iteration,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"then the order of dispatch is undefined."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"It is a no-op to call this function on a [struct","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Source"},{"type":"text","text":"] which has"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"already been destroyed with [method"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GLib.Source.destroy"},{"text":"].","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This API is only intended to be used by implementations of [struct","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Source","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":"].","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Do not call this API on a [struct"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Source"},{"type":"text","text":"] that you did not create.